data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful updated home ready to move into. Great location and area. Nice fenced in yard. Garage has lots of storage. Partially finished basement with extra bedroom and closet. Large Rec room also. Spacious family room just finished with new floors, trim and paint. Previous owner moved laundry to a first floor bedroom but can be moved back. They also installed a handicapped shower in addition to the tub in the bathroom. Could be perfect for anyone wanting first floor living. Upstairs bedroom has two rooms and lots os storage.  Hardwood floors in most rooms thru out home.  Roof and Furnace 2018, AC 20023, Hot water tank 2021. Gorgeous home and area. Don't miss out on this one it won't last long.
***Check out the 3D virtual tour above, click on Virtual Tour!!!***
